19. Simone Cristicchi – "Quando sarai piccola"

A heartbreaking autobiographical lullaby Cristicchi sings to his mother who suffers Alzheimer's disease. "Quando sarai piccola" is a son’s promise to a mother losing herself, a tender attempt to hold onto what time tries to erase.
